.TH SPACEGL_DIAG.SH 1 "2026-04-19" "SpaceGL @VERSION@" "SpaceGL Manual"
.SH NAME
spacegl_diag.sh \- SpaceGL diagnostic scanner launcher script
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B spacegl_diag.sh
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B spacegl_diag.sh
is a Bash launcher script for the SpaceGL real-time diagnostic tool.
It automatically detects the PID of the running
.BR spacegl_server (1)
process using
.BR pgrep (1)
and launches
.BR spacegl_diag (1)
in a dedicated
.BR xterm (1)
window with optimized geometry (160x50), monospace font, and a black
background with green text appropriate for diagnostic output.
.PP
The script aborts with an error message if no running
.B spacegl_server
process is found.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Diagnostic launcher started successfully.
.TP
.B 1
.B spacegl_server
not running, or
.B spacegl_diag
binary not found.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR spacegl_diag (1),
.BR spacegl_server (1),
.BR xterm (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Nicola Taibi
